{"tid":1910984,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【立法會選舉|拋磚】反對初選","createTime":"2020-03-05T04:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T13:49:21.000Z","uid":28914,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd5cc6a3ad8f1b669ec54134354b5e3b70f96ba","tid":1910984,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOrYHvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOrYHvr.png&h=c7173ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n始終素人資源有限 究竟初選已經宣傳 定係提名期開始咗之後先谷資源去宣傳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上次 朱凱廸 羅冠聰 都係選前民調麻麻 結果當日谷上來 朱仲做埋票王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果唔初選 / 有有效嘅協調機制 今次真係等攬炒 <br />\n係我哋自己內部攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足點睇"},{"pid":"db1ac76f62becddedf1d8d5be4d3036d9da46831","tid":1910984,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36671838683c701028369459664bb2f8c3b4337a","tid":1910984,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b53e0a337c744da701b550fe8bf7f0fecf4cb40b","tid":1910984,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f65f4e82aa167d475c739a13ecd5ebb52f520aef","tid":1910984,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bc57c0d7c7aba68fc51c24a6a43b63e084182e5","tid":1910984,"uid":28914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"呀豬呀狗都出嚟選 呢個問題真係要諗"},{"pid":"582851999cfa96f9a1ca82db2421a3befed5